          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The vacuum coating procedure is as follows: the bell",
                "jar is evacuated to 10**(-5) torr. and then the Li",
                "evaporator which is filled with either 6Li or 7Li  is",
                "heated, and the nickel backing foil and monitor glass",
                "are simultaneously coated to the same thickness through",
                "the mask."
